<p>The Republican-led US Senate voted to overturn tariffs President Trump imposed on Brazil by terminating the national emergency he declared in July, approving the measure 52-48 on Tuesday . Lawmakers say the emergency declaration was issued in retaliation for Brazil’s prosecution of its former president, Jair Bolsonaro, and the Senate bill is the first of three tariff measures expected to be considered this week . The measure now moves toward the House, where prior attempts to end the tariffs have faced resistance from House Republicans .</p><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Senate schedule: Senators prepared three separate tariff bills this week, with the Brazil measure the first passage in that sequence .</li><li>House resistance: House Republicans have repeatedly voted to block legislation aimed at rescinding Mr Trump&#x27;s tariffs, making House approval uncertain .</li><li>Use of emergency powers: The Senate action specifically targets the national emergency mechanism the president used in July to impose trade restrictions, signaling congressional pushback on executive emergency trade steps .</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>President Trump administration: The national emergency declaration in July was used to impose tariffs in retaliation for Brazil&#x27;s prosecution of former president Jair Bolsonaro. (<a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3330696/us-senate-passes-bill-end-trump-tariffs-against-brazil'>SCMP</a>)</li><li>House Republicans: House Republicans have repeatedly voted to block action on legislation to end Mr Trump&#x27;s tariffs. (<a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/united-states/us-senate-passes-bill-to-terminate-trump-tariffs-against-brazil'>The Straits Times</a>)</li><li>US Senate (majority of supporters): Senators backing the bill advanced it as a way to rescind tariffs imposed under the July emergency declaration. (<a href='https://japantoday.com/category/world/us-senate-passes-bill-to-terminate-trump-tariffs-against-brazil2'>Japan Today</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://japantoday.com/category/world/us-senate-passes-bill-to-terminate-trump-tariffs-against-brazil2'>U.S. Senate passes bill to terminate Trump tariffs against Brazil</a> - japantoday.com</li><li><a href='https://www.reddit.com/r/inthenews/comments/1oiu44a/us_senate_passes_bill_with_republican_support_to/'>US Senate passes bill with Republican support to rescind Trump’s tariffs on Brazil</a> - reddit.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3330696/us-senate-passes-bill-end-trump-tariffs-against-brazil'>US Senate passes bill to end Trump tariffs against Brazil</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/united-states/us-senate-passes-bill-to-terminate-trump-tariffs-against-brazil'>US Senate passes Bill to terminate Trump tariffs against Brazil</a> - straitstimes.com</li></ul>